---------------------------------------------------------------------
steps

Step 1 — NLB created
→ my-nlb-123.us-east-2.elb.amazonaws.com

Step 2 — CloudFront created FOR NLB
→ origin = NLB ✅
→ get: xxxxxxxx.cloudfront.net

Step 3 — WAF created FOR same CloudFront
→ protects same CloudFront ✅

Step 4 — WAF attached to same CloudFront
→ same CloudFront now has both:
   → NLB as origin ✅
   → WAF as protection ✅

Step 5 — Link WAF to Shield Advanced

Shield Console → Protected Resources
→ Select: xxxxxxxx.cloudfront.net (same CloudFront)
→ Associate WAF Web ACL
→ Select: my-cloudfront-waf (same WAF) ✅
→ Save ✅

Step 6 — Add CloudFront to Shield Protected Resources:

Shield Console → Protected Resources → Add Resources
→ Resource type: CloudFront distribution
→ Select: xxxxxxxx.cloudfront.net (same CloudFront) ✅
→ Add ✅
